title: 10 Takeaways from Week 7
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 7
description:
With DJ on a 14-hour flight back from London, the great Rhett Lewis and Bucky Brooks share their 10 biggest takeaways from a fantastic Week 7 of NFL action, including – Philly isn't special yet (1:00), the Jags have lost their identity (4:00), AD, ALL DAY, still has juice (10:00), the Rams did and will continue to deliver (12:30), rejoice Colts fans, Luck is BACK (16:00) & resolve is the Saints best trait (24:05)!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
